Appify is a tool to allow for the creation of Virtual Appliances-on-demand, 
in order to allow user applications to be run inside virtual machine 
sandboxes, while still maintaining a reasonable level of system usability.

This tool is a member of the family of OSCKAR-based products.
More about OSCKAR: http://clarkson.edu/projects/virtualization/osckar/

https://github.com/oopsigotroot/OSCKAR/appify

